name: 路易斯·克里夫
name_full: 路易斯·克里夫 Louise Cliffe
introduction: Cliffe, dubbed "Manchester's Kelly Brook",[1] was born in Middleton, Rochdale.[2] Cliffe attended Our Lady's' Catholic High School in Higher Blackley, where she was a talented athlete, becoming Manchester Hurdles Champion on three occasions.[citation needed] She still enjoys athletics and credits that as helping her keep her body in shape.In 2006, Louise won Miss Manchester.
